MADJDEF 106 hulking

MNUMBER 18
ADJECTIVE 106
NAME brute
HUMAN
GENDER 0
*DESCRIPTION_START
The hulking brute is a blue-skinned, humanoid creature with four arms
and two heads. His form is clad in a purple tunic and short green pants,
odd accoutrements for a monster. Bloodshot eyes and a natural sneer in the
brute's expression accentuate his nasty disposition.
*DESCRIPTION_END
STRATEGY 201
WEAPON 544 -1 100
WEAPONPLUS 300
ATTACK1 300
SPEED 1
BODY 260
ARMOR 44
DEFENSE 13
TEXD grabs his throat, makes an "ackkk" noise and topples like a felled tree.
RESIST 10

