*DESCRIPTION_START
A tree dominates this section of the manor yard, a dead and twisted tree
with bark hanging in strips from the trunk and branches like withered brown
vines. The tree does not come close to the manor wall which surrounds the
yard, its few remaining branches far too short. You notice something
disturbing about the building, now that you are near it- there are no
windows on the ground floor, only above, on the second.
*DESCRIPTION_END

IFPREVERB DIG -1
        CLEARVERB
        ECHO PLAYER You dig a little.
ENDIF

IFVERB RECALL -1
        ECHO PLAYER The tree reminds you of a story you heard when you were a child, about a ghost who was trapped in a dead mayten. All it wanted to do was laugh...
ENDIF

