*DESCRIPTION_START
This cramped hall makes you want to hunch your back and walk bent over low to
the floor. It's not that the ceiling is low, but it... feels low. As though
it could come a little further down at any moment, and then a little bit more,
and slowly creep down to crush you. Abandoning such thoughts, however, you
look around, observing the front door of the dilapidated structure, as well
as a coatroom off to the side. The hall leads north, towards a dining room.
*DESCRIPTION_END

